
Davis Center for Psychotherapy is an association of independent Counseling and Psychological Services mental health professionals with offices in Davis and Sacramento.  Its members provide a broad spectrum of psychological services to individuals, couples, adolescents, and groups.  Areas of specialization include depression, anxiety, relationship problems, grief, adult survivors of dysfunctional families, eating disorders, and life transitions.  A variety of insurance plans are accepted.  Private pay clients also accepted  some fee adjustments are available.


 Davis offers a wide variety of Counseling and Psychological Services.
